Purchase and Sale.On the terms and subject to the conditions contained in this Agreement, the Seller agrees to sell, convey, assign and transfer his Shares to Buyer, and Buyer agrees to purchase the Shares from Seller, effective as of 12:01 a.m., Eastern time on the day after the Closing Date.
  
