Phantom Stock Plan Payments.  At the Closing, the Buyer agrees to make either a capital contribution or loan to the Companys Subsidiary, CJ Systems Aviation Group, Inc. (), in an amount equal to $4,250,000, to assist CJ in satisfying its obligations to the PSP Participants.  The Buyer shall cause CJ to make the payments required under the PSP.  Within 30 days after the Closing, CJ shall pay to the PSP Participants $3,825,000 (less applicable withholding).  At the Closing, Buyer shall cause CJ to pay $425,000 to the Escrow Agent for possible future payment to the PSP Participants under the PSP and in accordance with the terms of the Escrow Agreement.
  
