Interest Payments
(i)           . Interest on Base Rate Advances shall be due and payable monthly in arrears on the last Business Day of each month. Interest on LIBOR Rate Advances shall be due and payable in arrears at the end of the applicable Interest Period but, in any event, no less than every ninety (90) days.
