Air Methods Corporation (the ) hereby establishes the Economic Value Added Bonus Plan (the ).  The purpose of the Plan is to measure financial performance of the Company in terms of Economic Value Added (), and to provide those executive officers identified in Section 7 below (each a , and collectively, the ) with incentive compensation based upon EVA results achieved during the Performance Period (as defined below).  The Plan is intended to encourage initiative, resourcefulness, teamwork, motivation, and efficiency on the part of the Participants that will result in financial success for both the stockholders and the Participants.
