On November 5, 2009, Air Methods Corporation (the Company") announced financial results for the quarter ended September 30, 2009. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report. The information contained in this report, including Exhibit 99.1, shall not be deemed "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, nor shall information be deemed incorporated by reference in any registration statement, proxy statement, or other report filed under the Securities Act of 1933 or the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, unless the Company specifically incorporates that information into those documents by reference.
