d by such Liens incurred as a result of such purchases shall at no time exceed the amount provided for in Section 9.2; (h) Liens disclosed on Schedule 6.4 and Schedule 6.6; (i) statutory or common law landlord's Liens to secure payment of rent so long as, with respect to the 7301 South Peoria, Englewood, Colorado location (the "Denver Facility"), such Lien is subordinated to the Liens in favor of Agent on terms reasonably acceptable to Agent; (j) Liens on Aircraft, other than Unencumbered Aircraft, securing aircraft indebtedness; (k)mortgage on the Denver Facility, provided that the Consolidated Debt secured by such mortgages does not subject any Borrower or its Consolidated Subsidiaries to any financial covenants, and (l) Liens on assets acquired in a transaction permitted by Section 9.5 and not created in contemplation of such transaction.
 
 
